## Navigating the interface
Areas I got familiar with:

- **Splunk Bar** (top) — messages, settings, search activity, help, and find;
  also switches between installed apps.
- **Apps Panel** — installed apps; Search & Reporting is the default.
- **Explore Splunk** — quick links to add data, add apps, and reach the docs.
- **Home Dashboard** — empty by default; pick a built-in dashboard or build
  and pin your own.

